  "title": "[✈️TRAVEL OPP |URGENT HIRING ✈️] CAMPAIGN MANAGER",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company</strong>: Eminence Organization</p><p><strong>Employment</strong> <strong>Type</strong>: Full-time</p><p><strong>Position</strong>: Entry Level | Immediate Start Available</p><h2>About the Role</h2><p><em><strong>Eminence Organization</strong></em> is a dynamic and fast-growing outsourced sales and marketing company partnering with established brands to expand their market presence through face-to-face marketing campaigns.</p><p><br />We are looking for enthusiastic individuals to join our growing team, helping brands grow and connect with people, and we want YOU to be part of that journey!</p><h2>Key Responsibilities</h2><ul><li>Represent client brands at roadshows and event sites</li><li>Engage customers through direct, face-to-face interactions</li><li>Deliver clear, professional brand messaging</li><li>Work collaboratively with team members to achieve campaign targets</li><li>Participate in continual training and personal development</li></ul><h2>What We Offer</h2><ul><li><strong>Comprehensive training provided</strong> for self development </li><li><strong>Structured mentorship</strong> from experienced team leaders</li><li><strong>Clear career progression</strong> based on performance</li><li><strong>Uncapped performance based incentives</strong> with weekly payouts</li><li><strong>Culture</strong> - Fun, supportive, positive, and team-oriented</li><li><strong>Travel opportunities</strong> - both local and overseas</li></ul><h2>Requirements</h2><ul><li>Strong communication and interpersonal skills</li><li>Comfortable with public interaction</li><li>Willingness to learn and improve</li><li>Able to thrive in a fast-paced, high-energy environment</li><li>Positive, driven, and hardworking mindset</li><li>Self-motivated and goal-oriented</li></ul><h2>Why Join Us</h2><p>This role offers hands-on experience, fast learning, and career advancement opportunities in a dynamic sales and marketing environment — ideal for individuals seeking growth beyond a conventional entry-level role.</p><p><em><strong>📩 Apply now to kick-start your career with us</strong></em>!</p>",
